      "title": "LLM Provider 策略",
      "aliases": [
        "Strategy",
        "Provider",
        "LM Studio"
      ],
      "summary": "通过统一 Provider 接口切换 Mock、LM Studio 和 OpenAI-compatible 实现，降低 AI 接入风险。",
